shit, so i just wrote an entry and deleted on accident. ill try it again though.

i had too much fun.  i loved every single second of the smokey mountains.
and when i was in virgina visiting my family, i felt like i belonged there or something. even though its a smalll ass town. i just love the mountains and nature.
ive realized im a very outdoory kind of person. i think ive always known it, but after this trip, i plan on living it. i love adventure, trying new things, and meeting new people. i cant wait to get out of here. but i know ill miss all my friends a lot :(
white water rafting was by far my favorite. it was such a blast. i plan on going on class 5s. (a class six rapid would be like niagra falls)(a class six rapid becomes a class 5 when someone survives it.)
we were just on class three and four rapids.
and my tour guid, matt, was AMAZING.
i fell deeply infatuated with him.
he was like all about some soccer. and he was really flirtatious with me! i dont understand why though ... 
what evvv.
but i hate how the first guy that comes around and likes me, or just guys that are hot in general i jump at. ITS LORAIN COUNTIES FAULT.
lasfjjkasdhfkjd i liked him so much. he's kinda the one that made me realize i need to persue my dreams of adventure and shit even though i love the city life. i mean shopping is like so much fun. i could never give that up. but for a summer job, going to tennessee and being a white water raft guide sleeping in a tent sounds really appealing.
askdfjaskldfj WHY do i have to be so youngggggggg.i feel like the only guys i like are olderish in college, even though i only really like one, but they are just so much more matureish and they like know what they want, thats very attractive to me. add goofyness to that. 

non of that really made sense or came out that way i wanted to, but i guess you get the over all point?

so i went shopping and got these heals and they're so cute! but i cant wear them until my knee gets better :(
which could be a while
but that gives me time to buy an outfit to match them!
i love shopping. i really do.

i had two people approach me about my knee. and they had knee problems too. they showed me their stiches. it was nice because i love it when people are nice. 
it gives me hope.

i just slepttt soooooo much. 
i got home last night really late, and didnt go to sleep till really late. but my mom still made me go to school. and i had all this stuff planned out today that i had to do. and i have homework, sorta, but im not actually going to do it. im going right up to my bed after i write this and going to sleep.

florida was so much fun. i realized a lot of stuff down thhere. we stayed on this island and it was the bomb. i gained back all the weight i lost, which kinda sucks, but whatever. i tried so many new things. like osterige(sp?) and parasailing. the guys there were in their 20s mostly, so i didnt get a chance to hook up with anyone :/ i mean i talked to people but i didnt like chill with anyone. next time i go on a trip, im bringing a friend becuase then i can socialize way easier. i spent a lot of the time by myself. which is fine. i joged two miles each day on the beach! and i would eat icecream and read books. kinda lame but whatever. it feels like so much happened down there, i just cant remember any of it. i want to go back sososososo bad. 

i have more important things to write about. but im so tired. so im going to go to sleep. im going to write them down somewhere else and get back to it.
